OL,6,FDomestic Abuse, and I am very pleased
OL,7,Fthat following that, the Domestic
OL,8,FAbuse Law
OL,10,F2024 is nearly ready for submission.
OL,12,F"This significant piece of work will
OL,13,Fgo a long way toward protecting
OL,14,Fvictims of these horrible offences,
OL,15,Fand ensuring our courts and law
OL,16,Fenforcement have the powers to punish
OL,17,Foffenders."
OL,19,FThe aim of these new measures is to
OL,20,Fprotect victims, their families, and
OL,21,Freduce the risk of reoffending.
