OL,6,FThe committee say it would also like
OL,7,Fto get into more schools to spread
OL,8,Fawareness of domestic abuse, build on
OL,9,Fthe new sexual assault referral centre
OL,10,Fand eventually update existing laws
OL,11,Fand legislation.
OL,13,FLast week members of the committee
OL,14,Fattended the first Violence Against
OL,15,FWomen and Girls symposium.
OL,17,FDeputy Aldwell added: "Joined up
OL,18,Fthinking and multi-agency working is
OL,19,Fvery important to tackle the
OL,20,Fwidespread issue of Violence Against
OL,21,FWomen and Girls.
